assetDescriptions.description:
Description

A private swimming lesson is designed to maximize the individual instruction given to a particular student with a one to one student/teacher ratio. Semi-private lessons are available for family members or close friends that have students of a similar ability (first student pays full private fee; second student pays at half price. Enroll the first child to secure the spot and enrollment of additional swimmers will take place the first day of the lesson). Refunds are not available for lessons; however, a credit can be provided. For swim lessons, please use the side entrance to enter the SLO Swim Center.

Refunds are NOT available for Swim Lessons, however credits may be provided.
